data.description: Nothing to do but move in! Greet your friends and sit a while on the welcoming rocking chair front porch of this southern charm beauty. Peacefully nestled on a large level lot in a well-established friendly community with NO HOA. Inside will not disappoint. You'll appreciate the practical layout with tons of natural light. Entertain in casual style in the vaulted great room graced with a lovely fireplace. The formal dining room will be the place you will gather with friends and family to make those wonderful memories. Escape to the spacious master retreat with dual vanities and tub/shower combo. All large secondary bedrooms provide privacy for guests or plenty of room for family sleep and play. With mature plantings and a nice amount of green grassy space for play, the outdoor space will not disappoint. Enjoy peaceful crisp air mornings on your screened-in porch or lazy day weekends in the spacious, fenced-in backyard- perfect for kids, pets and those family gatherings! FULLY FURNISHED. NEW Roof and HVAC. Move in today and start making memories tomorrow!
